      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a rare find that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like finish and not a single scratch, chip, or swirl mark to be found. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the upholstery, dashboard, and carpets showing zero signs of wear and retaining that fresh new-car scent. Every mechanical component and electronic feature functions perfectly, reflecting the meticulous care and climate-controlled storage this vehicle has received. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection, this car offers an unparalleled ownership experience.",
