    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really solid shape! It runs like a charm and has been well-loved, so it's ready for many more adventures with you. It's perfect for ziping around town or heading out on a road trip. Come take it for a test drive\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, both recently serviced to ensure optimal volumetric efficiency and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a functional M-Variable limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014a vital preventive measure for this chassis. The suspension is sorted with upgraded bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing excellent lateral stability and damping characteristics. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering a pure, analog driving experience with sharp throttle response and precise turn-in.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Title in hand. Ready for immediate use.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 luxury sport sedan that strikes the perfect balance between performance and refinement. The exterior is finished in a deep Obsidian Black that retains a high-gloss shine, with only minor road peppering on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the pebble-grey leather seats are firm and free of cracks, and the original floor mats have been protected by all-weather liners since day one. Every electronic feature, including the high-resolution navigation system and the premium surround-sound audio, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers smooth, responsive power. I have kept a comprehensive folder of service records, showing regular synthetic oil changes and recent brake pad replacements. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the suspension remains tight and silent over bumps. This car has been smoke-free, pet-free, and garage-kept, offering a premium driving experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a distinguished opportunity for the discerning buyer. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, it offers a refined driving experience that exceeds standard expectations for its class. We invite you to experience the superior handling and sophisticated presence of this exceptional automobile, now available for immediate acquisition.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my reliable ride, and it has honestly been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's totally ready for its next adventure with you! Everything runs smoothly, and it still looks great parked out front. If you're looking for a dependable car that has tons of life left and won't break the bank, this is definitely the one. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see how great it handles!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist's specification, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 mated to a 6-speed manual transmission. The engine exhibits exceptional health, pulling cleanly to its 8,400 RPM redline with the characteristic induction note of its individual throttle bodies. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and upgraded throttle actuators. The chassis retains its precision via Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a tight M-Variable limited-slip differential. While showing minor cosmetic road wear consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization and suspension kinematics remain sharp, offering a communicative and visceral driving experience.",
